				\begin{document}$${\text{NH}}_{{4}}^{ + }$$\end{document} at a high voltage during charge/discharge processes leads to irreversible reaction and structure degradation. In this work, partial NH4+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
